choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
For breakfast, I recommend having oatmeal with fresh fruit and nuts. For lunch, you can have a salad with grilled chicken or tofu, quinoa, and vegetables. For dinner, try making a stir-fry with brown rice, veggies, and lean protein like shrimp or tofu. Snacks throughout the day could include yogurt with granola and fruit, hummus with carrots or cucumbers, or nuts and seeds for a quick energy boost.
